  <brief_title>Early Tracheotomy Versus Prolonged Endotracheal Intubation in Intensive Care Unit (ICU) Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Early Tracheotomy Versus Prolonged Endotracheal Intubation in Intensive Care Unit Patients</official_title>
